### Existing Code Context

`adapters.rs` has `SseAdapter` with `broadcast::Sender<SseEvent>`, `subscribe()`,
`to_sse_event(RuntimeEvent) -> SseEvent`, `impl EventConsumer`. It maps all 12
RuntimeEvent variants to `SseEvent { kind, run_id, data }`.

`routes/mod.rs:build_router` assembles all route groups including `.merge(sse::routes())`.

`routes/sse.rs` serves `/api/events` and `/api/sse` reading `DashboardEvent` from
